{
  "id": "adv_group_moon_01_01",
  "title": "月のテンペスト 01 01",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "千紗、もう始めても大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ are you ready to start?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 3.6437188147999997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "うん。でも……昨日は月ストのライブだったよね\nお姉ちゃんは疲れてないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. But… wasn't there a Moon Tempest live yesterday?\nAren't you tired‚ Saki?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.8400002161,
      "endTime": 11.4103854814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫、しっかり寝たから\n他のみんなは元気一杯なのに、私だけ休んでられないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm fine‚ I got plenty of sleep.\nI can't be the only one resting when everyone else is full of energy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.6066668827,
      "endTime": 19.7317010242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんは渚ちゃんと、芽衣ちゃんは怜ちゃんと\n出かけてるし……あ、そういえば",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono went out with Nagisa‚ and Mei went out with Rei.\nAnd… oh‚ right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9279824255,
      "endTime": 27.3886174199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんはライブのMCを考え込んで\n寝不足だったみたいで、ぐっすり寝てるんだっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu stayed up late thinking about the live MC‚\nso she's sound asleep‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5848988213,
      "endTime": 33.664218584400004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、すずちゃんらしいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ that sounds like Suzu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.8604999857,
      "endTime": 36.6328129129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、私達二人一緒に取材なんて……\nこういうお仕事もあるのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But still‚ for the two of us to have an interview together…\nI guess this is another part of the job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.9,
      "endTime": 44.1288671171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "「人気の姉妹アイドル、白石沙季・千紗の素顔とは！」\nなんて大げさなタイトルになるみたいだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like they're going with the grand title of \"Popular Sister Idols‚ Saki & Chisa Shiraishi: Unmasked!\"\nBut…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.3333333333,
      "endTime": 52.5186178521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "お父さんが家族写真をデータで共有してくれてて\n良かったよね。今からアルバムを探すのは大変だし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad Dad shared the family photos with us digitally.\nIt would have been a pain to search through albums now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.7,
      "endTime": 61.5453758234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんと取材を受けるのも、アイドルになる前の\n話をするのも初めてだから……ちょっと緊張する、かも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's my first time being interviewed with you and talking about things\nfrom before we became idols… So I'm a little nervous‚ maybe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.7333333333,
      "endTime": 72.0482325868,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんみたいにしっかり受け答えしないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to answer properly like you do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.2333333333,
      "endTime": 76.33333328559999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "きちんと準備すれば大丈夫\nそのために今日は家族写真を見る訳だし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It'll be fine if you prepare properly.\nThat's why we're looking at the photos today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.5333333333,
      "endTime": 82.68115790639999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん、そうだよね\nよし……頑張ろっと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yeah‚ you're right.\nOkay… Let's do this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.8666666667,
      "endTime": 87.9536071772,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10799.999999999996,
          "startTime": 93.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、それじゃあ始めよっか\nまずは小さかった時から……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ alright then‚ let's begin.\nStarting from when we were little…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.1666666667,
      "endTime": 94.53333333329999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "これは……幼稚園くらいの頃かな？\nお姉ちゃんが私をぎゅってして一緒に寝てる……えへへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is… from around when we were in kindergarten?\nYou're holding me tight and we're sleeping together…Ehehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.2333333333,
      "endTime": 105.2480968788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "こっちは……千紗のお遊戯会ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And this one… is from your school play‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.4666666667,
      "endTime": 108.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "わわっ、私は村人の役なのに……\nお父さんてば、すっごくいっぱい撮ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa‚ I'm playing a villager…\nDad‚ you took so many pictures.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.0333333333,
      "endTime": 116.1033808067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、私の写真もある……\nふふ、千紗のこと、とっても心配そうに見てる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ there's a picture of me too…\nFufu‚ I'm looking at you with such a worried expression.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3,
      "endTime": 123.79063692029999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "たぶん海であのことがあった頃……だよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This must be from around the time when that thing happened at the beach…right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124,
      "endTime": 128.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "次の写真はおうちで……\nあ、お父さんとお姉ちゃんとホラー映画を観た時だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The next picture is at home…\nOh‚ this is from when we watched that horror movie with Dad and you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.9666666667,
      "endTime": 136.4974852873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "これを撮ったのはお母さんかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did Mom take this one?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.7,
      "endTime": 140.0259411335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "千紗は目をキラキラさせてるのに、私は泣きながら\nお父さんに抱きついてる……怖過ぎて覚えてないかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ your eyes are sparkling‚ but I'm clinging to Dad while crying…\nI was so scared I don't even remember.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2333333333,
      "endTime": 148.3916348452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "こうして見ると……お姉ちゃんと私って\nほんとにずっと一緒にいるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looking at these… you and I‚ Saki‚\nwe've always been together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.6333333333,
      "endTime": 154.8188230508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、そうね\n千紗が生まれた時から、ずっと一緒だったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ you're right.\nWe've been together ever since you were born…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.0333333333,
      "endTime": 161.86242875989998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "（私と千紗は年子だったから、物心ついた頃には）\n（「妹」という存在が当たり前になっていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Chisa and I are only a year apart‚ so ever since I can remember‚)\n(\"little sister\" was a constant presence in my life.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.1666666667,
      "endTime": 171.72771259860002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "（両親は共働きで、二人で留守番することが多かった）\n（幼い千紗は、両親がいないととても心細そうで……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Our parents both worked‚ so we were often home alone together.)\n(Young Chisa seemed so uneasy when our parents weren't around…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.1666666667,
      "endTime": 183.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_01_01-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "私がお姉ちゃんなんだから、しっかりしなきゃ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to be strong‚ because I'm the older sister!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.3333333333,
      "endTime": 186.9611564954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
